title.narrative: Comoros - HIV - Ministry of Health, Solidarity and Gender Promotion of the Union of the Comoros

description.narrative: Comoros - HIV - Ministry of Health, Solidarity and Gender Promotion of the Union of the Comoros - DNLS. This program has the following goals: End the AIDS epidemic in the Union of the Comoros by the year 2030. The objectives of this program are: Reduce new infections by 50% by 2019. Ensure that 90% of people living with HIV are on treatment by 2019
